These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, cooking, fishing, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, thriller, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, swimming, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, quad-bike, trike
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
 2. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 3. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 5. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person watching zombie movies is between the person driving the car and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 9. the person driving the trike is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
13. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
14. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person who's sport is cricket##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography     | cooking   | rock-climbing | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | zombie   | satire   | thriller  |
| Sport         | cricket  | swimming  | rugby  | skateboarding |
| Transport     | helicopter    | quad-bike | car     | trike    |

