.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, tea, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: tomato, plum, watermelon, eggplant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, ambient, techno, dubstep
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hedgehog, hamster
 1. the fan of techno is between the owner of the bird and the fan of ambient##2
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 4. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 5. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
 6. the person eating eggplant is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of punk is the owner of the cat##1
10. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
11. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the fan of techno##8
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
14. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
15. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
17. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
18. the person eating plum is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
19. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk  |
| Food          | eggplant     | plum | tomato | watermelon  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | techno  | dubstep | punk |
| Pet           | hedgehog | hamster | bird    | cat  |

