 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 5. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
 7. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

