 3. the person eating kiwi is the bartender##1
 4. the person eating onion is between the mechanic and the photographer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the writer##1
10. the photographer is the person who's sport is skiing##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
12. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4

