 4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 5. the person driving the helicopter is the australian##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the american##8
 7. the person drinking fanta is not the brazilian##6
 8. the police-officer is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking fanta##7
 9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
10. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
11. the doctor is on the right of the mechanic##1
12. the police-officer is not the malaysian##6
13. the american is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
14. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
