.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, gospel, d&b, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, basketball, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, taxi, trike, motorbike
 1. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 8. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite   | soy-milk     | milk    | cola |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | hip-hop      | d&b     | gospel     |
| Sport         | biathlon | basketball  | water-polo     | handball  |
| Transport     | ship     | trike | motorbike | taxi     |

