.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, hot-chocolate, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, cooking, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, blues, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, japanese, indian, pakistani
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the pakistani##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
 3. the person drinking water is the fan of gospel##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the indian##3
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
10. the fan of blues is not the australian##6
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the fan of punk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
14. the australian is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade        |
| Hobby         | reading | writing   | camping   | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | gospel   | blues    | hip-hop      |
| Nationality   | japanese   | pakistani | indian   | australian    |

