.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, tea, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, journalist, fisherman, bartender
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, bird, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, taxi, trike, roller
 1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 2. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the journalist##8
 3. the owner of the dog is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
 6. the person driving the roller is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the bartender is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
 8. the fisherman is on the far right##1
 9. the journalist is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
10. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
12. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
13. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the bartender##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk          | hot-chocolate | tea        | lemonade    |
| Job         | bartender | nurse   | journalist | fisherman  |
| Pet         | bird           | dog     | ferret       | mouse  |
| Transport   | roller            | trike   | taxi     | tram |

