.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, milk, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, baking, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, security-guard, manager, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, trike, motorbike
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person drinking milk##6
 2. the doctor is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the doctor is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
 6. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the manager##8
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the paramedic##7
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | milk        | iced-tea        | hot-chocolate        | juice   |
| Hobby       | chess      | woodworking      | singing | baking |
| Job         | paramedic | manager | security-guard     | doctor  |
| Transport   | trike          | airplane      | bike     | motorbike  |

