.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking, woodworking, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic, writer, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie, disaster, horror
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, funk, classical, d&b
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the scientist##8
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 4. the accountant is the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the writer##6
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
 7. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the writer##8
 8. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 9. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
11. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the writer and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | woodworking   | writing   | filmmaking |
| Job           | scientist | paramedic    | writer | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | time-travel | zombie     | horror    |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | classical      | funk         | d&b     |

 